    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are helplines. i've called them. they just tell me to \"hang in there\" or \"take a deep breath.\" but breathing just hurts too. it's not like a bad mood you can just get over. it's my body. it's just broken. i'm so tired of fighting a war that i was never meant to win. it feels like there's no point to any of this anymore.",
