    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "specialists, doctors, more treatments... it's all just more noise. they all promise things will change but they never do. it's just a cycle of trying something new and then the pain comes back even harder. i look at people who are healthy and i just feel like i'm living in a different reality. i just want the noise to stop. i just want it to be quiet. i feel like i'm just waiting for an end that won't come.",
